description: A spectacular and idyllic one of a kind penthouse duplex with expansive open and airy 4,383 sq.ft. of space in the Seaport. This house in the sky balances chic architecture, privacy, and spectacular living space with soaring 13 ft ceilings. Exuding luxury and sophistication with a sunny southwest corner exposure while balancing warmth, an inviting ambiance, and a make-it your own stunning flexible interior. The main floor features custom baltic birch flooring, original brick & Carolina pine beams and a professional stainless steel chef's kitchen. A gracious curved staircase leads to an incredible triple gabled roof house w/ a master bedroom suite, magnificent bathroom & dressing room, second kitchen, sitting room and a custom built sound studio, all with direct access via large glass panel doors to a large private roof terrace. This unrivaled unique home can be used as your residence & is also zoned live/work w/ direct freight elevator access. One parking space & storage included.
